{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Mandate whole life orders for people who rape or murder women or children",
        "additional_details": "Rape or murder of women and children is predatory, not a mistake. We think these offenders act on deep-rooted, dangerous behaviour that cannot be cured, and that releasing them gambles with lives and retraumatises victims. The Government\u2019s first duty is to protect the innocent. We think permanent containment is the only way to ensure safety and justice for women, children, and families.",
        "background": "Legislate so that anyone convicted of the rape or murder of women or children can never be released. Such offenders should face indefinite containment with no parole or early release, putting public safety and victims\u2019 rights above offender rehabilitation.",
